**File:** `/home/rich/git/foci/command/builtins.go`

**Examples:**
- `/log` — shows last 20 lines (default), `/log 50` — shows last 50 lines
- `/errors` — shows last 10 lines (default), `/errors 25` — shows last 25 lines

